'''ecces''' in [[Quenya]] means "to find out, bring out by examining, or eyeing[?]"<ref>[[Parma Eldalamberon 17]]</ref>
==Etymology==
Older Quenya and [[Vanyarin]] ''ecceth''.

Possibly it incorporates ''[[et]]'' "out of" + ''[[ces]]'' "search"
